            "cave": {"default": ["Still air carries mineral damp and the sound of water far below.", "Cold drafts move through unseen cracks while grit shifts underfoot.", "The cavern dark stays heavy, broken only by echoes and distant dripping."]},
            "forest": {"default": ["Oakwood shade gathers thick around the trail, full of wet leaves and birdcall.", "A soft rain taps through the canopy and turns the forest floor dark.", "Sun shafts break through the boughs while undergrowth steams from earlier showers."]},
            "mountain": {"default": ["Thin wind scrapes over the Mistcloak slopes and makes every ledge feel exposed.", "Clouds snag on the peaks and spill cold mist down the trail.", "Clear mountain light shows distant ridges, but shadow brings a quick chill."]},
            "plains": {"default": ["Open farmland wind bends the grass and carries the smell of worked earth.", "A broad fair sky hangs over the fields with only distant weather at the edge.", "Fast showers sweep across the open ground and leave the road shining."]},
            "river": {"default": ["The river runs high and brown, pushing foam against roots and stones.", "Cool mist rises off the water while reeds whisper along the bank.", "Bright light flashes across the current and hides sudden depth."]},
            "road": {"default": ["Dust lifts under passing boots and wheels, then settles into old ruts.", "Cloud cover dulls the road while distant tree lines blur in damp air.", "The track is clear for now, but every bend hides the next bit of trouble."]},
