            "urban": {"default": ["Busy streets hold the day's warmth while smoke, rainwater, and cooking scents mix in the air.", "Cloud cover dulls rooftops and turns every alley sound close.", "Fair weather brings open shutters, market noise, and dust under cart wheels."]},
